How to use?
1) Set the vm.max_map_count: https://www.elastic.co/guide/en/elasticsearch/reference/current/vm-max-map-count.html
2) docker-compose build
3) docker-compose up
4) Check out https://pypi.python.org/pypi/python-logstash and use the code shown in there. TCP connections are accepted at port 5005, UDP at 5006
4.5) Drop some log messages (important for step 5)
5) Go to localhost:5601, log in as elastic/changeme
6) Click on Discover, pick @timestamp as the time event and click create.

Voila, you can play now.

